Ten thousand thanks for these Matrix's!!!!!!!! This show is a keeper.
check out the supplication.

11-04-77
12-01-79

Terrific sound... Love this show.  Love the aud/sbd mix from Mr. Chappell ("Sick!).  Love the way the boys sounded end of 82.  Love those pre-New Years shows.  Love the way they played: energetic, relaxed, creative.  Good one!

Best Lazy/Supplication ever this is a great show, but really the stand-out is the lazy lightnin, supplication, One of the best in terms of quality and style. It starts to get away from the boys towards the end of the supplication jam, but they still pull off, and even with the rough edges it still is sweet as honey
My favorite show This is my favorite show that I saw live. Morning Dew was one I waited for a long time and finally got it on this night.
